IMPORTANT - which FFmpeg build to bundle
----------------------------------------
Only bundle an LGPL build of ffmpeg.exe. Do NOT bundle a build compiled with
--enable-gpl (for example builds that include x264/x265) or with
--enable-nonfree, because:

  * A GPL build would require this entire application to be released under the
    GPL.
  * A "nonfree" build cannot be legally redistributed at all.

This app only stream-copies audio and embeds a JPEG cover (ffmpeg -c copy). It
does not encode audio or video, so a minimal LGPL "shared" or "essentials"
build is sufficient. Recommended sources for LGPL Windows builds:

    https://ffmpeg.org/download.html   (see the Windows builds linked there)

